Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew Helen, who did the interdictation on the course, and I knew Bill Thepford, and Steinbergs, Saul, who published it for the Foundation for Inner Peace, and his brother, and his brother lost a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I lost my thumb, his brother came out to be with me, because he thought I'd probably be grieving the loss of an amputation, and he'd already been through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought that was a very loving thing to do. It was Paul, who was not deceased, and so it's all, you know. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier you said that sometimes people will willingly agree to take on the karma of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that just high-level teachers, people of high levels of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also wondering, you said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we saw the Pope do it to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope did that to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of all sinners, he was doing it. I could read his mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of all sinners, he was doing that as a sacrifice to the Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was obviously a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that women are more non-linear than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that they calibrate higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, recently there was some research about the IQs of men and women, alleging that men were higher than women or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we instantly, I intuited that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't as good as science.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's completely false. No, it wasn't that. It was IQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's false. Their IQs are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I asked you a question, it was about surrendering thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one day it just came to me. I'm not going to follow my mind all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you told me about staying on the razor's edge, and so I went home, and I tried to do it, and you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There were some amazing states of joy, like the more you love God, the more you feel it, and then there was this feeling of insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like I was going backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute now. You've got to go slower. I'm talking to the microphone. Don't give me a batch of confusion. Straighten it out. Linear, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There were these feelings of feeling like I was going backwards, like I was headed in the wrong direction, because it almost felt like insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you used to be insane, and you're going backwards into it again? What do you mean backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt all this lower, like that joy wasn't there. It was, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean lowered state, lowered state of consciousness. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It felt like I was headed in the wrong direction with the surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surrendering every...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were just allowing some negative, negative material to come up, to get cleared. I told you that. When you get high, when you're above your karma, you feel high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're now above your karma, you've earned the karmic credit to handle a bigger stack. So what comes up then is a bigger stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that you're going backwards, but you're not. You're just handling what would have been too much for you to handle prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you read the lives of the Christian saints, especially the women, many of them are saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They wrote their biographies. They would go into a high state, and then they would lose it because the next stack would come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would go into mourning and feel deserted by God. So many of the great famous, especially women mystic saints, you really, really, you've got to read about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you won't, you know, think that you're unusual or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you recommend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have a list of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a list of spiritual teachers. In that spiritual teachers, you see several.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In Encyclopedia Britannica, look up mystics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see some of the famous women mystics, a number of whom really were proclaimed to be saints, who would reach a high state and then crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can you have deserted me, my beloved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is far and parcel of the mystic course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to look it up in Encyclopedia Britannica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up mystics, and you'll see there's about half a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of all of them, you can read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Magdeburg, many, many famous ones, German ones, Austrian ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's par for the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've earned the right to say how awful you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, I have been awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christmas miracle of your presence here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm basically up here to step through a fear today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All's well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look in the presence of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's afraid to come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she had a.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's come to see us since 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been an impetus to come and kneel and acknowledge all that I'm grateful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want a year to pass again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people cry for a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And monastic orders, that's very well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reach a certain level, you cry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to only cry when I saw love expressed in one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A loving glance, and I couldn't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A kitten looking up with trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying lasted for, I don't know, a year or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an experience a few years ago where I was in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it changed my whole, it seemed like I lost my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And a couple days after the accident, when I was recuperating,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this overwhelming, incredible experience of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, there was so much love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seemed that at that time that I couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, it was just way too much love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's almost as if I just shut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I noticed recently a recurring belief or pattern within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I allow the love that I feel inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the lovingness that I feel inside to be expressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,or shown, or revealed, or all of those whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'll get, it's like I would be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that pattern, it seems to have reared its head recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a tendency to want to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What I would be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal I would be crushed, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You would disappear into that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true, you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My body might just topple over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing serious, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems like that's kind of where I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically the ego is worrying about its survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So just if you surrender to dying, it'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because pretty much every day I say I surrender my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disappointed that it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so I can just let it rip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have family or friends or associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody who knows what you're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so they realize that it's a spiritual state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also been the desire over the last year to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like just, I want to go and be in seclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and just be one with God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's nothing else that really appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be in seclusion anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the stage you may well go through, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So regardless of response, I mean, I'm single, I don't have a cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any plants, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I have financial responsibilities, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So take advantage of the fact that I'm single,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a cat or any plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the financial responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that you have to make do as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You could sell manure, all kinds of things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty bucks a load.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably up to sixty by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rent you my manure truck for 25% of the profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your old truck? Your old truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, that thing sounds scary to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no power steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I had one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that power anything though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a Chevy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're doing all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep telling me I'm doing all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess I'm just going to have to take you for your word on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you may not be able to function,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll put you in the poorhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll all support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you too, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even find a poorhouse anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dickens days, they had poorhouses and workhouses and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they do, and they have a poorhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chino Valley has houses that they maybe retreat in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You might contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing to me that there's a person that does work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they have that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the monastic life sometimes comes up as an option in people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an amazing gift to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you both so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, when I'm here, Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the presence of God through you, and I feel so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and it feels so easy to have that faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when I go home, I pray and try to do the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have this intellectual knowing that God is real,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have faith because I hear what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have such faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard for me to really feel God a lot of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's really painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, that's normal, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after a while, it gets stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you can envision the group or the teacher or, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,high moment with the group to sort of recapture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it becomes more and more predominant as time goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The separation feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, the feeling of the presence of God that becomes more strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In a group like this, of course, it's very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after you leave the group, your memory of the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,your vision of the group, et cetera, will carry you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the group affiliation doesn't require a geographic location,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be in the middle of the Pacific,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you're a member of some great group like AA or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, that carries you through because your commitment is one of commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's geographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So hold the group in mind to reconnect with the feeling here of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, to hold it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the whole group in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Hawkins, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that I've noticed every time I come to ask a question
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is an awareness of, like, that black spot on your soul thing you talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any black spots?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any black spots?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like when I sit with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a black spot on your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, more like just a subtle, like, nervousness or guilt or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know I'm, okay, I'm juicing it, it's narcissistic, but it's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to admit that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should feel guilty about having unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to feel guilty about worrying about a black spot on my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, scrupulosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her I had to go for counseling with the priest about scrupulosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if there's any kind of technique to, like, clear energies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that you pick up in your chakras or your aura throughout the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That you pick up when?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, throughout the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You may pick up certain energies from people or different things that get stuck in your
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,aura or your chakras?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thump the thymus and think of God or Jesus or some divine figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else, like prayer or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Holy Spirit revealed to you what the energy, negative energy, is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the Lord to impress upon my mind the awareness, the knowingness of what kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,energy is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then from that, you can assume which chakra and maybe what kind of an archetype
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,within.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you said, too, that, like, these energies that come from out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of within, we've got the, I guess you could say the karmic right to demand that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the karmic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, I hereby order you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the power of the Lord Jesus Christ within me, I order you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you tell the dark spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the dark spirit, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that to the dark spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thanked you both many times in my consciousness, but never face to face, in protoplasm, so from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the depths of my heart, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this gift of love and appreciation from myself and Elinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the one that hollered out, get a second opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it came from that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the previous guy kind of took my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thymus thump I found to be incredibly useful, you know, for spiritual first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just throughout the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For a quick thumper, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I don't know if people realize how useful that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As I ask people, do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It works amazingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a quick fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious about the energetics of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on when you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thymus is right behind the breastbone of a breastbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The thymus controls the level of killer cells in the immune system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to do with the balance of the acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So if something negative comes along, it can blow out that acupuncture meridian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it was John Diamond taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was the thymic thump, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can activate the thymus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It then pours out more killer cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It pours out more good neurotransmitters and gets you out of a negative fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you're angry at somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't seem to get off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You just smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Works great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you brought it up because I tend to forget mentioning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you gave up sugar and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when my friend elbowed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have been diagnosed with depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that took a long time to admit that and to have a crisis that it actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got medication for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I am on medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly want to give up sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hereby ordered to surrender your willfulness, choose the purity of God's help as your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem is you got to go withdraw from the sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But do it after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very scrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me to do it, I will do it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:22:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you things you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But any words you can use instead of sugar, that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have peanut butter for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Peanut butter, peanut butter and crackers, you'll find that it knocks out the desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It works.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the other thing that I used to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Peanut butter and, oh, pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pickles, well for some reason you feel like you got to have something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet and sour pickles, is that the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread and butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread and butter kind of pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, bread and butter pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll find it works
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and it works
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it works for pregnancy too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so this doesn't include
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,like giving up bread
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that kind of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,no that's more severe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I did that one year and it was really difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah that's more severe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you give up all white starch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're trying to get off sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can avoid white starch on an empty stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's advisable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words anything that releases
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your blood sugar is going to go up like this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you eat sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your blood sugar goes up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,then you pour out insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,now the blood sugar skyrockets it down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,normal people let's say their blood sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,starts at 95 they eat something sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,goes up to 114
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly comes back down to 95
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,people like yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they eat sugar and sweets suddenly it shoots up to 160
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then it rockets down the insulin pours out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes down to 90
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,85 by 85 you've got the shakes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're psychotic
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinking about suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and we used to do serial electro EEGs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I had a big clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we would do a five hour glucose tolerance test
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.71,0:24:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd take a big dose of sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we would do an electroencephalogram
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,periodically every half hour or so
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for six hours
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.76,0:24:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and chart the blood sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.26,0:24:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and as it came down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.76,0:24:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd see the EEG
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,go right into dysfunction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at one time we had a lady
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:24:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a little job
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.75,0:25:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that told the group once before
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that her blood sugar skyrocketed down
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in the meantime the medical profession
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is boo-pooing this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.36,0:25:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway so
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.54,0:25:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as it came down
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.93,0:25:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she got more and more psychotic
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.52,0:25:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and her EEG became very desynchronized
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.23,0:25:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and when her blood sugar got down to about 70
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,she tore all her clothes off
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.39,0:25:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.43,0:25:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and man has it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the traffic was pulled over to the curb
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,on all sides
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.02,0:25:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lab director was about 6 foot 4
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,like Ichabod Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.49,0:25:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,big tall skinny guy with a long white coat
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.49,0:25:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's running down the sidewalk after her
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.49,0:25:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,come back Ms. Connors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.49,0:25:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,come back Ms. Connors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.49,0:25:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's running naked down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the traffic is all piled up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.76,0:25:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and people are telling me they don't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.76,0:25:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.76,0:25:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say yeah right
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.22,0:25:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have been tested before a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.22,0:25:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but not for five hours
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.22,0:25:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but they didn't come up with anything
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.22,0:25:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so while I'm doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.22,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I should stay on my medication
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:25:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's empirical
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,just cut out sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.22,0:26:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and see if it doesn't help the need
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.22,0:26:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,depression
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.22,0:26:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes that's all that's necessary sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah but she should stay on her medication
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I should stay on my medication
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.38,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah I would stay on my medication
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can try tapering that later
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.38,0:26:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but first try and get hold of the dietary aggravation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.38,0:26:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.34,0:26:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,no it's no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.34,0:26:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,get lots of peanut butter and pickles
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.34,0:26:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and do what I say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop being rebellious
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.34,0:26:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.48,0:26:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can have your toys back again
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.48,0:26:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting it where her teddy bear and her scooter
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.48,0:26:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so she can be complies
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.48,0:26:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is this your water
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.48,0:26:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,water water
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whose water is this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.48,0:26:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,someone forgot it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah there you go
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,someone forgot their water
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.22,0:26:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.22,0:26:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.20,0:27:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.58,0:27:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time I was here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.58,0:27:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,was a year ago October
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and you had bagpipes playing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.58,0:27:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and they played Amazing Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.58,0:27:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all experienced 535 energy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.58,0:27:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which was wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.58,0:27:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we did it Sunday at St. Andrews this week
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.58,0:27:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,oh did you do that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.58,0:27:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,last week yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.58,0:27:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother has arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.81,0:27:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,an Amazing Grace for four part acapella
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.81,0:27:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and we did it with male voices
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.81,0:27:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and it sounded just wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.81,0:27:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to give the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.81,0:27:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that version
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.81,0:27:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,oh Amazing Grace yeah thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.81,0:27:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and just a warning
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.81,0:27:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was part of singing this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.81,0:27:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and just hearing it the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,brought me to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.81,0:27:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just so wonderful beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.81,0:27:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,oh thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.03,0:27:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.03,0:27:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.03,0:27:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the question I have is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.03,0:27:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you taught about hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.03,0:27:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and then had to stop teaching about hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.03,0:27:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because it came back for you I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.03,0:27:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,yes I gave it up you know see
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.09,0:28:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I was giving lectures on hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.09,0:28:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,well that re-established it as a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.09,0:28:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,operative reality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.09,0:28:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I had
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.09,0:28:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to change my course
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.09,0:28:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.09,0:28:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,psyching myself back into it myself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.74,0:28:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because the average person
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is subject to it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but a person more advanced in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.74,0:28:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,will begin to cancel it out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.74,0:28:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you keep reaffirming it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.94,0:28:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as an existing reality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.94,0:28:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll begin to experience it out again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.94,0:28:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.94,0:28:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you had to quit it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done 12 step groups
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.94,0:28:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was my first foray into personal growth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.94,0:28:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I did a personal growth workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.94,0:28:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which was really
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.94,0:28:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the next step for me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and helped me an awful lot
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I came to your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.94,0:28:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the third step for me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.94,0:28:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm in the process of learning how to teach
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.94,0:28:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the personal growth course
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.94,0:28:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm wondering because it's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.94,0:28:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit different than your teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.94,0:28:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and your teaching is of course higher level than that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.94,0:28:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,by teaching that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.94,0:28:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,would it have some sort of impact in
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.94,0:29:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my work in working with this information
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.16,0:29:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why it should
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.16,0:29:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is the truth no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.38,0:29:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.55,0:29:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,can I get a picture with my wife and my mother and father with you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.55,0:29:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,sure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.55,0:29:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.58,0:29:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.58,0:29:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah they're all here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.58,0:29:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,mom and dad can you come up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.58,0:29:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.58,0:29:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your arm quick
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.75,0:29:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding on my calvary is over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.75,0:29:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,personal growth is over 300
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.75,0:29:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,personal growth is over 300
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,400
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.98,0:29:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's 350, 360
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.98,0:29:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.39,0:29:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,personal growth is not going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.05,0:29:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll grade as high as the course of miracles or AA
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are y'all in there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.05,0:29:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and five
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that it's great for positive attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.08,0:30:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,benevolence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.20,0:30:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.20,0:30:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.20,0:30:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.16,0:30:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,working on about ten to four
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.90,0:30:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the line is still quite long
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.90,0:30:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah okay we'll move along
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.90,0:30:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.90,0:30:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.90,0:30:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and appreciate everything you've done
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.90,0:30:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.90,0:30:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.42,0:30:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,door number one or door number two
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.42,0:30:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or door number three
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.42,0:30:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,good to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.42,0:30:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.64,0:30:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor is good to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.64,0:30:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan good to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.64,0:30:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,your work is fabulous
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.64,0:30:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just started into it recently
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.64,0:30:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,since my divorce two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.08,0:30:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,attracting a woman into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.70,0:30:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,from a romantic heart to heart standpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.70,0:30:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,give it up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.94,0:30:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,now he's still got a negative camera left
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.94,0:31:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,go ahead yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.57,0:31:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the story about it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.80,0:31:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well that's probably the answer right there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.80,0:31:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that's probably the answer right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.65,0:31:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender. Oh, he comes celibate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.73,0:31:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.73,0:31:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling him, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.28,0:31:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the problem about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.63,0:31:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, kidding aside, what is the problem about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.23,0:31:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be paradoxical intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.04,0:31:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradoxical.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.84,0:31:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradoxical intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.45,0:31:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it paradoxical?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.86,0:31:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm interested in the gal, she's not interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.52,0:31:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if she's interested in me, then it doesn't work for my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.09,0:31:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a one-way relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.20,0:31:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll agonize its way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.59,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the right one doesn't come along every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.16,0:32:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in circulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.55,0:32:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.72,0:32:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in circulation, that's my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.96,0:32:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.90,0:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hooked up on one frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.85,0:32:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.75,0:32:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you appreciate the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.44,0:32:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It does come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.04,0:32:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all you ladies out there that are single.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.94,0:32:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a neat-looking specimen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Mark and Ansel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.09,0:32:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I thought I'd reverse the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.25,0:32:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I wrote this book, I decided to autograph it and present it to you for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.42,0:32:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the Cajuns, my people in South Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.94,0:32:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The healers, the traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.88,0:32:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather was a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:33:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I spent about 10 years researching the book and throwing it away and writing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.48,0:33:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, it was published about eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.51,0:33:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to read the autograph to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.48,0:33:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.68,0:33:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, to Dr. David Hawkins and all his miracles, Cajun miracles included.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.18,0:33:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.24,0:33:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak a little bit of Cajun for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.53,0:33:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Vous parlez français, Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.40,0:33:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vous parlez pas français?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.22,0:33:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't speak French.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.38,0:33:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.83,0:33:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have mine with toast on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.00,0:33:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.33,0:33:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have a question, but I do have a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.14,0:33:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For the previous speaker, you know, like you said, you get into this spiritual path and look out and things might happen in your family, in your marriage and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.55,0:33:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was married to a woman after five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.48,0:33:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a great relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.85,0:33:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.14,0:33:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We studied with you for the last three or four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.01,0:33:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then about eight weeks ago, she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.90,0:33:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a paradigm change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.06,0:34:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our marriage ended, and our separation and divorce, and living by myself in a little cabin in a Cajun country now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.94,0:34:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a lot of freedom to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.26,0:34:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of freedom to that, living by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I could choose to suffer, or I could choose freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, your book says that so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.78,0:34:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the freedom, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.82,0:34:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.84,0:34:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.21,0:34:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we got another one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.96,0:34:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.38,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're raffling them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.80,0:34:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A dollar a raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.09,0:34:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.15,0:34:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.88,0:34:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.92,0:34:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold that down?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.44,0:34:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.59,0:34:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.11,0:34:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.96,0:34:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.46,0:34:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.15,0:34:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.88,0:34:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.59,0:34:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.53,0:34:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.30,0:35:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.90,0:35:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.38,0:35:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.19,0:35:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.46,0:35:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.76,0:35:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.15,0:35:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,From all my...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.90,0:35:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From the depth of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.55,0:35:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.01,0:35:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You answered so many questions already, but a friend asked me to ask you, would that be
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.53,0:35:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.30,0:35:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend asked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.21,0:35:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.01,0:35:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.71,0:35:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this friend of mine is Reverend Jack Blackman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.13,0:35:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a religious science minister in Albuquerque, and he's been having some experiences where
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.76,0:35:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he starts seeing the presence of God in other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.03,0:35:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gets a little overwhelmed, well, a lot overwhelmed sometimes, and he wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.26,0:35:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if he would stop being overwhelmed, or if it would progress in a certain way, or what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.26,0:35:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,would...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be answered, but that is a certain state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.21,0:36:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in it myself one time when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.26,0:36:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the divinity of all, everything shines forth, including its perfection and its beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.15,0:36:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you often start to cry quite a bit for a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He does.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.48,0:36:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He does cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.46,0:36:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.26,0:36:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.96,0:36:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.01,0:36:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfectly okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.86,0:36:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.50,0:36:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have it in airports.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.05,0:36:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd see the people look at each other, and I'd start to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.15,0:36:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.69,0:36:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.30,0:36:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.13,0:36:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, the community of your students who are gathering here in Sedona to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.57,0:36:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,does this serve a group purpose or another purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:36:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.50,0:37:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The people that are gathering here, where we live, does that serve a group purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.78,0:37:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're just attracted to each other, you know, because of commonality of goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.53,0:37:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, having a commonality of goal, and they naturally form their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.32,0:37:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they form a spiritual community is what they do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.09,0:37:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.44,0:37:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's common throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.05,0:37:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual groups tend to congregate in certain places, and often from there,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.05,0:37:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it then spreads forth again back into the world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.42,0:37:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.65,0:37:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.53,0:37:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.07,0:37:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.86,0:37:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.59,0:37:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.73,0:37:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.55,0:37:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.34,0:37:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.88,0:38:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the on switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're more non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.75,0:38:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.61,0:38:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are more non-linear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.05,0:38:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.65,0:38:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's not something that had been done in time but.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're seeing the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.30,0:38:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the printing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.26,0:38:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.30,0:38:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.88,0:38:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.28,0:38:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.44,0:38:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you and Susan and your staff for all the fine work that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.53,0:38:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Very appreciative of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.71,0:38:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Question I have is you mentioned again today that we as a group swoop in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.23,0:38:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.92,0:38:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.44,0:38:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you mentioned that in Dayton, I think, a couple of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.90,0:38:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.94,0:38:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all going to do, complete our work in unison that we need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.30,0:38:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we have a saree and then we both do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A loose affiliation of camarade, of commonality, of intention
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.86,0:39:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that tends to bring us in and out collectively, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.17,0:39:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.42,0:39:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like ice ages, et cetera, tend to favor, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all the blackbirds coming at a certain time,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's not going to be favorable for blackbirds
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.17,0:39:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for another couple hundred years, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.69,0:39:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so they tend to flock in when times are propitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.13,0:39:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe to uphold the level of consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.11,0:39:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,under difficult times.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.36,0:39:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be so that a group like this is here now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.23,0:39:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to help uphold mankind under difficult and trying times.
