Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.86,0:39:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When things are rosy and swell, they don't need us here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.34,0:39:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so we go back and rest on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.88,0:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.69,0:39:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the cheer-up squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.96,0:39:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means we have some additional work
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:39:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.44,0:39:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do, yeah, that sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.73,0:39:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.88,0:39:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.44,0:40:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think perhaps a sustaining function
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.46,0:40:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so as to prevent human despair worldwide, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.59,0:40:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think to offset human despair worldwide, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.38,0:40:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because cataclysmic events could bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty widespread despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.98,0:40:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, yeah, you've mentioned, I know, in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.69,0:40:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that with the end times sort of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.11,0:40:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that that relates to the lower ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.80,0:40:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.28,0:40:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all the prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.36,0:40:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.73,0:40:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.15,0:40:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this has nothing to do with prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.11,0:40:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the unfoldment of the potential of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.76,0:40:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the higher power uses anything in its own service.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.78,0:40:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's willing to sacrifice the small self
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.17,0:40:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of the large self, or the capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.01,0:40:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.90,0:40:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Man's calamity is God's opportunity, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.61,0:41:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people turn to God as a result of Katrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.05,0:41:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've got nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.53,0:41:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But God, sometimes that's what it takes to find God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.01,0:41:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This question is about my son's allergy to nuts and eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.78,0:41:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my first lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I realize there could be a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.76,0:41:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that he won't be allergic anymore.
