Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.19,0:41:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's physical allergy to nuts and eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.36,0:41:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So what has it got to do with consciousness and God?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.11,0:41:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.48,0:41:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my world right now, I want my son to be healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.53,0:41:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
