Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.78,0:42:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see she's asking a general question.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.63,0:42:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Except he can't eat the nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.50,0:42:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an X recommended in the diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.19,0:42:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but it's a blood-type diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.92,0:42:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So following the...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but this isn't a good book, then, if he can't even do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.26,0:42:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
