Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.36,0:42:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know if this diet is going to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.61,0:42:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.15,0:42:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for God's sake, woman, just put him on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.61,0:42:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'll either get better or he won't.
