Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but supposedly certain blood types react differently to certain foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.26,0:42:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to listen to all that stuff.
