Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.46,0:46:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the planet think God told them to kill I don't pay attention to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.13,0:46:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that but then it's an unfortunate chapter I never cared for it there's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.59,0:46:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,much truth in the Bhagavad Gita but not that particular one but it's also
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.26,0:46:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated at 900 I think you calibrated pretty high not that chapter oh but but
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.84,0:46:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in the Bhagavad Gita all about the battle scene what is the battle scene
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.42,0:46:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,got to do with your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.25,0:46:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just giving me an academic question well it's like nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.05,0:47:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with your life what does it mean to you it's about asking me the question it's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.11,0:47:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,about you're not on the battlefield you're not belonging to either side so
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.84,0:47:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you asking me the question it's about doing a duty what is my duty about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.32,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,my life it would depend on what your level of consciousness is at one level
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness your duty would be to take up arms and fight for what you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.53,0:47:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,think is right in another level of consciousness it would be your duty to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.96,0:47:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not participate
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.28,0:47:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so it would depend on what your level of consciousness so my objection to that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.42,0:47:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,chapter is is that what level of consciousness are you talking to see
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.13,0:47:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what's correct at this level to back off from your duty to be brave to stand to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.63,0:47:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,stand for what is right etc at another level would be wrong then at another
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.84,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,level it becomes right again so the context changes with the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.36,0:47:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness another level of consciousness is idiotic the whole story
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.71,0:47:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,take my word for it's idiotic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.71,0:47:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,got it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.88,0:48:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ok thank you very much you have your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.03,0:48:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i'm glad glad that it confused you it's a good sign
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.63,0:48:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody reads the Bhagavad Gita if that doesn't bother you the whole
