Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.65,0:48:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not very serious seriously yeah because there is no actual personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.84,0:48:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,doing that so there are various levels you can interpret that there is no
