Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.59,0:48:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,self-killing enemy that's all in your mind it's okay it is a miracle to be in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.92,0:48:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,dr hawkins yeah i want to thank you for being my teacher thank you my pleasure thank you too
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.48,0:48:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah the first chapter of the bhagavad-gita boggles everybody's mind what in hell they're
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.65,0:49:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about everybody says hello dr hawkins yeah thank you for all that you give us
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.34,0:49:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you um i'd like to ask for your blessings on my life you have it thank you and um i'm on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.96,0:49:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the precipice of a very large life-changing decision and i would just like to ask is it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.90,0:49:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,truly in the highest and greatest good to end my marriage highest good to what and your marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.78,0:49:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and my marriage i don't know if i'm allowed to ask it yeah i'm not allowed to ask it or just
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.13,0:49:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.15,0:49:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because i'm robbing you of the karmic significance and impact and earning earning about it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.44,0:49:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,some things i can't all i very often personal things i gotta know because it interferes with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.73,0:49:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's karma if i'm feeling say 99 complete i should probably go with that feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.53,0:50:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and trust my inner the problem is one of doubt huh i'm talking about a relationship there is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.09,0:50:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,no certainty in a relationship because it's whatever the two of you make it to be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.51,0:50:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you can start out awful and get fantastic or you can start out fantastic and get awful you know so
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.63,0:50:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,uh it's a whole training program so learn my lessons it's a whole it's you know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.55,0:50:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it helps mature people i think relationship like that because when you're married now you're up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.48,0:50:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,against it for real you've got to really make peace or you're really going to have war and you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.48,0:50:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,can't just play around with it you've got to really face it and do what you can and you can
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.57,0:50:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,be centered in love and part lovingly if that serves the highest part lovingly no not always
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.51,0:51:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah thank you it's a big casino in this world isn't it yes yeah roll the dice you take the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.96,0:51:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,chances big casino okay thank you bless you yeah it has big lessons though too big benefits thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.23,0:51:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,big upset
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.03,0:51:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and big downside risk yes um i don't have a question i just wanted to be in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.19,0:51:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you thank you very much uh-huh gives me herself as a gift huh yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.88,0:51:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,here's one of the mad elves
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.11,0:51:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell by the mad look in his eye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.51,0:51:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,actually all questions uh basically well they did dissolve on the way up here but i didn't want to
