Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.78,0:52:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the opportunity to say thanks and uh it influenced this life greatly and uh my privilege and a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.19,0:52:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful group here in sedona i've had the privilege of living here for a short time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.86,0:52:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and a very inspiring amazing group all the way around and uh yeah i once uh you kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.65,0:52:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,influenced me when i lived in flagstaff i got a job for the catholic church cleaning the priest
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.69,0:52:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and a Newman Center, and this shirt right here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.82,0:52:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,was hanging on the wall, and I immediately thought of you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.44,0:52:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.21,0:52:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.63,0:52:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, the students, the Catholic students at NAU
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.17,0:52:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,wear this, it's one of their shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.48,0:52:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, I was like, that's Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.01,0:52:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As I always said, the greatest job on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.21,0:53:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is being a verger in a Greek cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.11,0:53:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so to be the verger at Church Cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.01,0:53:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be careful not to keep saying that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.03,0:53:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.09,0:53:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.03,0:53:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.34,0:53:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To serve God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.51,0:53:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.53,0:53:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.53,0:53:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not have a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.55,0:53:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just love being in the presence of both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.21,0:53:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.51,0:53:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also came across this CD,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.48,0:53:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.21,0:53:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tenor, and the sound, music,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.96,0:53:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just transcends and transports,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.71,0:53:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like for the two of you to have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.90,0:53:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.94,0:53:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know we love music.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.13,0:53:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.94,0:53:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.86,0:54:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to ask if I can have a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with my brother and the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.65,0:54:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.57,0:54:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.19,0:54:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.03,0:54:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, the second edition
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.94,0:54:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of Celtic Woman is out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.07,0:54:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.48,0:54:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out of focus, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.80,0:54:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert, you're better at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.05,0:54:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.55,0:54:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You need somebody with a more linear mind to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.57,0:54:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.57,0:54:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I should talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.57,0:54:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Dr. Hawkins, you've given us a lot to contemplate,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you were in Long Beach, I asked you the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.07,0:54:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you blew my circuits, and I couldn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.51,0:54:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't remember what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.51,0:54:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't received your DVD yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.42,0:55:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, can you expand on contemplation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.13,0:55:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.53,0:55:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.44,0:55:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.44,0:55:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation is a lifestyle where you identify
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.13,0:55:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with context instead of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.19,0:55:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your life becomes like a mudra.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.69,0:55:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life becomes invitational to God's revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.30,0:55:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of yang, like, I must get that,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.42,0:55:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've already defined in a linear design what it is you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.01,0:55:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A contemplative lifestyle is more accepting.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.30,0:55:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.30,0:55:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like, reveal to me, O Lord, that which...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.98,0:55:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's more thus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.00,0:55:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.00,0:55:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.00,0:55:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you notice the beauty and perfection of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.13,0:55:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice the beauty and perfection of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.63,0:56:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty and perfection of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.76,0:56:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.55,0:56:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.57,0:56:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the miracle of the rattlesnake
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.07,0:56:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,on the top of Shinnebly Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.65,0:56:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.65,0:56:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.15,0:56:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.57,0:56:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if I can put this into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.50,0:56:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading your latest book.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got towards the end of it where you were talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.00,0:56:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the final doorway and that type of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.00,0:56:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought that came into my head wasn't so much about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.00,0:57:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was the idea that any separate, independent thought
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.82,0:57:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was the separation that holds back the progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.75,0:57:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.75,0:57:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.75,0:57:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't necessarily hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.75,0:57:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It would just be reflective of where you're at with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.21,0:57:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't necessarily hold you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.21,0:57:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't necessarily stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.21,0:57:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.21,0:57:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an interesting thought that it was the,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.21,0:57:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of a good word,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.09,0:57:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the belligerence that separates
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.09,0:57:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by having an independent thought from God himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.76,0:57:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an illusion that it's an independent thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.40,0:57:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get over that, then you don't have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.40,0:57:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.07,0:57:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thought, but it's not your thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.07,0:57:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.07,0:58:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.07,0:58:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not yours, why worry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.23,0:58:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.23,0:58:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a free man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.23,0:58:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not shackled to the thought, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.48,0:58:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.48,0:58:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.48,0:58:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.48,0:58:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a passing bird in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.13,0:58:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.13,0:58:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.80,0:58:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.03,0:58:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.90,0:58:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.90,0:58:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.92,0:58:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.92,0:58:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.90,0:58:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.90,0:58:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.90,0:58:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell them the rattlesnake miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.90,0:58:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.03,0:59:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.03,0:59:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.03,0:59:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.03,0:59:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.03,0:59:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.03,0:59:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple questions, and it's probably-
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.03,0:59:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.03,0:59:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.03,0:59:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.03,0:59:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.57,0:59:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.57,0:59:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.57,0:59:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In general.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.57,0:59:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's probably non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.57,0:59:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's very non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.57,0:59:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.57,0:59:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.57,0:59:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Very non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.57,0:59:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.57,0:59:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.57,0:59:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you said that guilt is one of the locks to the miraculous, and it's self-indulgence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.57,0:59:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Any attachments, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.59,0:59:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.59,0:59:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, in one of your early lectures, I remember you saying when someone says they
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.59,0:59:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,can't do something because they won't, and they won't do it because it's too much effort-
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.59,0:59:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.59,0:59:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That someone won't do something because they can't-
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.82,0:59:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't do it because they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.82,0:59:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't do it because they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.82,0:59:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.82,0:59:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.82,0:59:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that they can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.82,0:59:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.82,0:59:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.82,0:59:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it says too much effort, because they're holding something back, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.34,0:59:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.34,1:00:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my question is, I do healing work, and one of my clients, her mother, was a really
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.92,1:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,bad alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.92,1:00:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, back off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.92,1:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.92,1:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.92,1:00:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he can't hear you when you-
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.92,1:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.92,1:00:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with willingness, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.92,1:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.92,1:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.92,1:00:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what I'm trying to understand is, the alcoholic who drinks, and the next morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.57,1:00:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they're very angry and enraged, and there's some that'll drink, and there's some that'll
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.36,1:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,drink, and they don't get angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.48,1:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, what I'm trying to understand, what makes one alcoholic really angry and furious
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.65,1:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,after they drink the night before?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.07,1:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're very abusive to their children, like, I hate you, you ruined my life, and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.38,1:00:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all those negative things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.69,1:00:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what makes one alcoholic angry the next day, and one not?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.86,1:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a very general question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.19,1:00:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It would depend on their level of consciousness, and their emotional condition, and their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.65,1:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a-
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.65,1:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.65,1:00:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer a question on that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.65,1:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.65,1:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in one of your earlier videos, one of the very first ones-
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.65,1:00:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not due to the alcohol, it's due to who the person is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.65,1:00:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.65,1:00:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In one of your earlier, very first videos that I had watched, you had explained something
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.65,1:01:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about it, but it was so long ago, I didn't remember, and I thought, maybe-
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.65,1:01:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have, in our A-B series, which is archival, we have a whole CD devoted to alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.65,1:01:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.65,1:01:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.65,1:01:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.65,1:01:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.65,1:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.65,1:01:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.65,1:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.65,1:01:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.65,1:01:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.65,1:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.65,1:01:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.65,1:01:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.65,1:01:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.65,1:01:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.65,1:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.65,1:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you wanted to add, that is something you probably should get.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.65,1:01:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.65,1:01:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's 19-something.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.71,1:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a whole CD, and it's devoted to alcoholism.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.38,1:01:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all my questions will probably-
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.38,1:01:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A good majority of them will be answered in that CD.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.38,1:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.38,1:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.38,1:01:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.38,1:01:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a puzzler.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.38,1:01:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.38,1:01:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.38,1:01:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's all the time we have.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.38,1:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.38,1:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for sharing your story.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.38,1:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.38,1:01:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.38,1:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.38,1:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.38,1:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.38,1:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.38,1:01:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.38,1:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.38,1:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.38,1:01:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.38,1:01:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.38,1:01:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.38,1:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.57,1:01:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.07,1:01:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to push it, but I think that that would answer a lot of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.03,1:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It would, definitely. Right. Because, like I said, one of his earlier,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.61,1:01:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it was one of the very first ones I ever watched.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.73,1:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He explained the difference between someone who gets angry after they drink
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.26,1:02:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and someone who doesn't. And I just couldn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.98,1:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There were so many CDs of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.71,1:02:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at that CD, that's a very good one on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.53,1:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the alcohol. Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.75,1:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's devoted strictly to that. It's about an hour and 20 minutes or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.32,1:02:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. Okay, thanks. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.61,1:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my magnifying glass. I guess they took it in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.90,1:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I took it. I put it in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.09,1:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.46,1:02:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.30,1:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something here for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.63,1:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.88,1:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago, I was in an abusive marriage and had a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.55,1:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he got involved in drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.63,1:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I left when my daughter was five, came to America.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.82,1:02:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just about to turn 32. And I might cry in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.28,1:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.44,1:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She, I raised her spiritually with the same teachings that you have.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.53,1:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's always followed that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.05,1:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, she had a friend who was...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.55,1:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,into drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.55,1:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And she decided that she would need to try the drug
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.44,1:03:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so that she could help him get through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.03,1:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And has been addicted to meth for the last 18 months.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.21,1:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I brought her out of that relationship,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.96,1:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was she, did she need that experience karmically?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.88,1:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And by me taking her out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.09,1:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,she's managed to find...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.73,1:03:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,almost...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.21,1:03:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,almost the same situation and duplicate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.46,1:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be the lesson wasn't learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.46,1:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be repeated until it's learned, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.55,1:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with her being...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.34,1:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the first step in Al-Anon
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.92,1:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is to let go and to control the other person.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.55,1:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, let go and to save them and control them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.28,1:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just depriving them of a karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.15,1:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're just going to have to go keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.28,1:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing that complicates it with her is because she still has the same...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.28,1:04:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual understandings.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.46,1:04:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.96,1:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her your consciousness and addiction CDs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.67,1:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.44,1:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.94,1:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not ready for them?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.05,1:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.55,1:04:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows them off by heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.78,1:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not ready for them?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.69,1:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.19,1:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She quotes them every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.05,1:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows exactly what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.28,1:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.76,1:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.07,1:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can she do is what she wants to save in China?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.94,1:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.84,1:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.40,1:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.34,1:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do at this point with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.90,1:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.25,1:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.17,1:04:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Join Al-Anon.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.01,1:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.80,1:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.67,1:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.38,1:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me take it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.40,1:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Anon is for...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.90,1:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Anon is for, like, children and alcoholics, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.96,1:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wives, spouses, family members.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.69,1:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spouses, family members that have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.59,1:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to join Al-Anon and follow the program.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.07,1:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.98,1:05:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.86,1:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just ask one more thing about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.42,1:05:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.19,1:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this karma...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.78,1:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she healing old karma at this point?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.88,1:05:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.38,1:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking an academic question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.30,1:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.57,1:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to S...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.07,1:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Al-Anon and take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.57,1:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her worry about her karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.57,1:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.57,1:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.09,1:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to worry about her karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.09,1:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her worry about her karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.09,1:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest thing for parents to do is stand by and watch your children understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.09,1:05:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, because you're taking on that which is beyond you and not controllable by you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.09,1:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.11,1:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should just let her get on with it and, and back out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.11,1:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Al-Anon and take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.11,1:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat back to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.11,1:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Al-Anon and take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.11,1:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Al-Anon and take step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.11,1:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me again until you do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.23,1:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to report back to this group that you went to Al-Anon and took step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.23,1:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.23,1:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.23,1:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.23,1:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to your sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.15,1:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to let go of controlling her, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.15,1:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.15,1:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.15,1:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.15,1:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.15,1:06:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll free her that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.15,1:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.15,1:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.15,1:06:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you hit the bottom quicker and harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.15,1:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.15,1:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.42,1:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.86,1:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just helping them limp along.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.86,1:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.96,1:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you a while ago about defenselessness and-
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.96,1:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.96,1:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Defenselessness?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.96,1:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.96,1:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.96,1:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, for about three days I felt nothing but love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.96,1:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then fears kind of came back and it went away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.11,1:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.11,1:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have it come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.11,1:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know what to do about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.11,1:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.11,1:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.11,1:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know what to do about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.11,1:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.11,1:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.11,1:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.57,1:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.57,1:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.57,1:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.57,1:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.57,1:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.05,1:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.05,1:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,do? I'd like to come back. She wants to know what to do about what? She wants that. Oh. I felt nothing but love. I've never experienced that before. I felt nothing but love for three days. I had no anxiety. Oh yes. I don't think anything. You see all spiritual evolution tends to be evanescent. Rarely do you go into a certain state and stay there permanently. It begins to fluctuate. And just accept that that's par for the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.92,1:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's par for the course. And just keep. It's normal. Yeah, it's normal. You'll get states of bliss coming back and then states of discouragement and then moments of renewed enthusiasm. And that's normal. That's normal. I'd just like it to come back. It was wonderful. It was wonderful. If you would just let go wanting it to come back, you would give the space to recur. Don't you get it? It filled you to the brim.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.15,1:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of it. Okay, I got it. Do what you tell you or else. I'm the Dutch uncle, the spiritual teacher, I'll tell you. Because it's more painless. Yes? I actually got up here without crying this time. Now you're going to cry. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.72,1:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The question that I have is about a very negative energy that came to me during the night. It's happened before. And I've always used your words that you said in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.77,1:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right, right. Yeah. And it's always been very effective. These episodes seem to happen after I'm in a very high state. And what I'm wondering is there something in me that's drawing this energy to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.19,1:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I just hate you because you're in a high state. Okay. It's envious. It was as if this last time that this energy came to me with a knowingness that I could choose this state. And there was in fact an attractiveness to the evil or whatever it was. There was an attractive to my ego recognized the attractiveness of it. But I... That's being called being beset by demons.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.94,1:09:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.59,1:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately, immediately rejected it and pushed, you know, rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.38,1:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because they don't know any better. See, and they're trapped in their domain. They're trapped in their realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.03,1:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.02,1:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trapped in their realm. And they're unwilling to do what it takes to get out of that realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.19,1:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.14,1:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, all you can do is have compassion for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.85,1:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.47,1:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the denial of the divinity of God is what keeps them there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.22,1:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't resist. It's the denial of the divinity of God. And you can't force the entity because you will have robbed it of the right to leave hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.75,1:10:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hellish.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.90,1:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hell, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.02,1:10:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw, I could see that it was hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.63,1:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the demons from hell, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.98,1:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.89,1:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower astral planes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.35,1:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I felt like I was almost visiting there. I don't know why, but it was during a dream or something. Or maybe it came to me. I wasn't sure. But when I woke, it woke me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.63,1:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.31,1:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very intense.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.09,1:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.56,1:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found somebody else to bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.28,1:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I did. And your words, your words helped me a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.67,1:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.63,1:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. I love you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.75,1:11:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.89,1:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this field.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.97,1:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the hell, hence demon, to your own domain. Accept Jesus Christ as your savior, and you will be free. It's his choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.56,1:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.26,1:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.64,1:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you say something for us about something you spoke about?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.35,1:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you've spoken about before, vertically aligned relationships?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.64,1:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Vertically, you see, the trouble with relationships is they tend to be horizontal. Solar plexus, interacting with solar plexus chakras. Control, control, control, control. Or seduction, seduction, seduction. Or right and wrong, better than you, you know, win, lose. All right. So that's the way, it's solar plexus, horizontal. Push, pull, control.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.77,1:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.60,1:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationship that's aligned like this is parallel. You're both aligned with the same ultimate goal. Therefore, you're always aligned no matter what you do. I hate you. I'm sorry I said that. Why did I say I'm hating you? You don't have to wonder if I forgive you. I understand, etc. See, they're both aligned to spiritual perfection, so they're willing to forgive anything. These people are going to carry a grudge. She got to choose what movie we're watching. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.15,1:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to stay up later to watch television later. See, it's record keeping and score keeping. So most relationships end up in squabble score keeping. Struggles over money and all those things. Control, in-laws. If you're both aligned in the same direction, you automatically find ways to heal that. I'm sorry I said that. I wasn't even thinking right. I don't know where my mind was at the time. And the other person is willing to forgive them because you're both aligned with forgiveness and growth.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.81,1:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And supporting each other's spiritual growth and development. You know, I'm interested in winning and losing. There's no winning and losing in a relationship. Because if you win, you're just lost. If you win, you're just lost. It's just a matter of getting even. All right, you had mashed pumpkin tonight. Wait till tomorrow, baby. You're getting fried squash. You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.68,1:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So any two people in a relationship who are committed to spiritual perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.71,1:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. So a company can be very, very aligned and very, very powerful. And they're all aligned with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.92,1:14:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.11,1:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Most companies are struggling for, you know, he wants to be vice president, he wants to be comptroller, and this one's jealous of that one, and he's got a corner office with two windows, and I only have the one window.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.34,1:14:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.59,1:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can get any organization aligned like that, it's going to be successful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.05,1:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And so then any group of people or any two people are capable of a vertically aligned relationship, provided they have that commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.78,1:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any relationship is possible that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.27,1:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To serve each other's highest purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.25,1:14:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is another way of saying, you know, serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.47,1:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.47,1:14:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That gets you out of power struggles. Most people in a relationship get caught up in power struggles.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.89,1:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So serving the highest good and serving each other's highest good is the way to get past that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.61,1:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes you parallel.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.64,1:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're never crisscrossing each other. You may strain each other, be short-tempered or something, but that doesn't change your goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.64,1:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal is not to be a short-tempered person. I mean, that's not your goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.97,1:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't change your goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.51,1:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.98,1:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Temporary blip on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.18,1:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So if you're both vertical, you're not going to change your goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.67,1:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.55,1:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.69,1:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.22,1:15:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.89,1:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I once knew a lady who was in a relationship, and every time her husband and her had a fight, she'd take his toothbrush and clean the toilet bowl with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.51,1:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So whenever you have a fight with your husband, change toothbrushes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.05,1:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.82,1:15:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a funny story.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.71,1:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan. I knew there was a reason I came here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.09,1:16:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She is now suffering in hell. You didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.59,1:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You better change yours when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.81,1:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank God for you two and for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.07,1:16:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a very simple question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.56,1:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For whatever reason, I'm not able to muscle test reliably, and I don't personally know anyone who is able to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.15,1:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.27,1:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a few professionals who use it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.61,1:16:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unable to muscle test their integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.85,1:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I go about using that as a tool for truth in my life?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.52,1:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.92,1:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.96,1:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried it with the heavy books.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.43,1:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried it with the two-person.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.69,1:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried it with this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.39,1:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.26,1:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.69,1:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's also karmic reasons sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.26,1:16:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.80,1:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And just maybe it's not the best thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.06,1:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're not supposed to be using it right now or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.15,1:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wondered about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.07,1:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.63,1:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.51,1:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're going to short-circuit a greater spiritual understanding that you're trying to bypass by quick answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.25,1:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wondered about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.39,1:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the sense of it I'm getting.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.39,1:17:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sense that I'm getting.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.81,1:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to use it to bypass spiritual understandings.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.00,1:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.89,1:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.40,1:17:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the books.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.71,1:17:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the books or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.56,1:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.72,1:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.07,1:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, your books?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.02,1:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My books, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.31,1:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.69,1:17:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.76,1:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose book is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.72,1:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been there a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.48,1:17:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.02,1:17:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Kockes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.38,1:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.84,1:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We came from cold, cold Canada.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.50,1:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing wind, minus 30 just to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.81,1:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Came from where?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.65,1:17:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Canada, minus 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.14,1:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.57,1:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting chilly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.82,1:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.72,1:18:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to say thank you for the continuous miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.14,1:18:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.60,1:18:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A million times a day, every corner I turn around, every minute of the day, looking in my daughter's eyes, in my pet's eyes, outside, in my clients, in the world, there is, I cannot say anymore because words are useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.77,1:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.56,1:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.75,1:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.03,1:18:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite animal?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.35,1:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, tough one.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.67,1:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough one?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.63,1:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you like horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.81,1:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I like horses and dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.85,1:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorns are wonderful, and dinosaurs I'd love, and kitties, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.85,1:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I drew you a picture of a horse and a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.02,1:18:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.64,1:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.39,1:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great artist.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.43,1:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.48,1:18:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.63,1:18:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.97,1:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.78,1:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.82,1:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.06,1:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.25,1:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.68,1:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.90,1:19:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's a cute dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.78,1:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dinosaur with consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.22,1:19:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cute dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.31,1:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.86,1:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.27,1:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought something for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.32,1:19:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.44,1:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.60,1:19:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereabouts in Canada?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.27,1:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamloops.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.82,1:19:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only four hours away north from Vancouver.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.90,1:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vancouver, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.93,1:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in Vancouver area this summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.35,1:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple months ago, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.59,1:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.82,1:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.93,1:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We fell in love with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.10,1:19:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.67,1:19:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.35,1:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We did the Inland Passageway.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.02,1:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inland Passageway was stunning, stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.10,1:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stunning, stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.21,1:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.21,1:19:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.21,1:19:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God, miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.27,1:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.27,1:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuous miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.27,1:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.27,1:19:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.27,1:19:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was incredibly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.27,1:19:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystical.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.39,1:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.39,1:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.39,1:19:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to finally meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.39,1:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.39,1:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you as well, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.39,1:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.39,1:20:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.52,1:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.52,1:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.17,1:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.17,1:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.17,1:20:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.17,1:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.17,1:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.17,1:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.17,1:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.17,1:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.72,1:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.03,1:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.03,1:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.81,1:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.52,1:20:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.27,1:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.92,1:20:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.31,1:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can I ask a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.19,1:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know you believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.69,1:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you're telling me is about eternal radio waves,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.67,1:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,am I in a position to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.56,1:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think I'm in a position in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.77,1:20:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I definitely want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.60,1:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.69,1:20:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me, can you tell me a little bit more about I
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.21,1:20:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,believe if I could type Glas Creature into
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.31,1:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,your brain?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.09,1:20:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.14,1:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.68,1:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to come up by itself anyway because your intention is going to set
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.89,1:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the instruction so when you try to be unconditionally loving you're
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.73,1:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically attracting energy up to the heart chakra pranayama calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.77,1:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,190 so there's a lot of yoga tricks that are actually injurious and you know I
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.40,1:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,would perhaps picture the ideal of what you would like so spiritual energy wise
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.35,1:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the ideal for you at this moment what do you want it to do go where the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.96,1:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,sensation I guess it's the physical sensation that there's a tangible
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.40,1:21:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,immediate spiritual effect or reward the buzzing in your fingertips you feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.81,1:21:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you've raised your body to a higher pitch a higher octet
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.55,1:21:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know in the moment that goes out this is the same thing if you show up
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.71,1:21:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your body going to go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.01,1:21:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.56,1:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.13,1:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, the body will respond to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.59,1:21:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the body is not going to become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.71,1:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,nor will it take you to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.11,1:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I would picture the energy more into energizing
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.38,1:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you wish to become,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.89,1:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart and the universal heart, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.18,1:22:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.02,1:22:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I do as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.85,1:22:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, up to the third eye, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.03,1:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you picture the energy rising up to the third eye
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.52,1:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to open the third eye of discernment,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.72,1:22:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which is really, you know, the third eye of the Buddhic body.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.27,1:22:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would not use any artificial means, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.56,1:22:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your intention is sufficient power.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.85,1:22:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy will flow up
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.81,1:22:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,based on your intention and your dedication.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.39,1:22:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose where this stems from is
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.27,1:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.85,1:22:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm still, when I'm being,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.65,1:22:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I'm making progress spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.46,1:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.38,1:23:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're not making progress?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.64,1:23:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I'm doing, then I'm not being,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.90,1:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.93,1:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have to be proactive.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.68,1:23:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to have a dedicated routine,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.64,1:23:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a dedicated practice, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.43,1:23:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and meditation, and those are...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.93,1:23:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, dedication is...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.22,1:23:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation is something you can do
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.34,1:23:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get past the point of...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.10,1:23:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,doingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.30,1:23:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.57,1:23:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have become doesn't need to meditate.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.50,1:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.93,1:23:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are is all that is already.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.77,1:23:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're well aligned.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.63,1:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.94,1:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be patient, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.72,1:23:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow yourself to be attracted
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.81,1:23:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of trying to propel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.76,1:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow yourself to be attracted by your destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.46,1:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of trying to propel yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.18,1:23:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.50,1:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.00,1:24:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The immense gravity of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.97,1:24:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is like pulling you,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.53,1:24:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and you allow yourself to let go of resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.14,1:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to propel yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.86,1:24:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.68,1:24:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're moving fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.21,1:24:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going bald already from a lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.18,1:24:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I get bald slower.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.59,1:24:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.27,1:24:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All that effort, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.39,1:24:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to start off by saying
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.17,1:24:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Lubbock, Texas,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.32,1:24:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,my friend who has been coming here with me
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.56,1:24:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,asked me to tell you hi,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.81,1:24:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wishes he could be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.40,1:24:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.68,1:24:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.10,1:24:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.38,1:24:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have trouble discerning
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.51,1:24:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,whether I'm standing up for truth
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.21,1:24:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or engaging in, like,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.44,1:24:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,some sort of justified resentment ego juice.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.61,1:25:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Resentment?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.92,1:25:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so much, well,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.61,1:25:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,not so much resentment, but frustration.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.89,1:25:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's more like you stand for
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.27,1:25:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.06,1:25:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't require you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.94,1:25:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't require aggression.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.19,1:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll usually do that, like,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.26,1:25:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the act of standing up for truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.46,1:25:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but then afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.60,1:25:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I start reliving it in my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.23,1:25:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and kind of reworking it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.03,1:25:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Should have said something different,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.38,1:25:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,should have done something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.42,1:25:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you stand for what you understand
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.10,1:25:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.19,1:25:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At other times, you may see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.65,1:25:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.56,1:25:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you've become a different person by then,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.88,1:25:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you should take a different stance.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.26,1:25:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.22,1:25:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At one stance, it's wrong not to slay the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.30,1:25:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At another level,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.35,1:25:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why we were talking about the Bhagavad Gita.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.56,1:25:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd never understood that either.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.93,1:25:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.78,1:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Should he slay the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.98,1:26:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or should he refuse?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.52,1:26:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is his highest principle?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.42,1:26:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Lord, Juna.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.14,1:26:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.15,1:26:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.35,1:26:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at each level,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.01,1:26:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at each,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.82,1:26:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,period of spiritual development,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.01,1:26:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have a different answer
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.17,1:26:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of what's appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.10,1:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it kind of whatever I go through
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.46,1:26:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is appropriate unless I see it differently?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.14,1:26:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.22,1:26:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.06,1:26:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you may see it in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.85,1:26:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for many years,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.72,1:26:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and then slowly or suddenly
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.06,1:26:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you can change your mind about it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.97,1:26:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then I can just accept the way I handle it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.97,1:26:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.92,1:26:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.03,1:26:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.64,1:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's all transitory.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.26,1:26:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why worry about something
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.96,1:26:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's already a was,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.57,1:26:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not an is?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.57,1:26:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.57,1:26:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.34,1:26:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already a was.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.34,1:27:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up regretting the wuzzies.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.67,1:27:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The wuzzies?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.06,1:27:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was that way,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.06,1:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was that the way I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.06,1:27:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.06,1:27:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.06,1:27:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.34,1:27:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a couple of questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.34,1:27:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you guys talked about the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.34,1:27:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,other people picking up karma for other folks,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.59,1:27:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering if I could drop off a bunch of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.59,1:27:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you could put them in the depository box.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.59,1:27:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The depository box.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.43,1:27:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.43,1:27:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have a chute on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.43,1:27:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering what I can do to get away from the desire
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.60,1:27:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask you the right or the perfect question.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.60,1:27:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me the perfect question?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.60,1:27:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.60,1:27:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You already asked me the perfect question once,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.60,1:27:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so why do you want to ask it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.14,1:27:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.17,1:27:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.17,1:28:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.52,1:28:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.52,1:28:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.77,1:28:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're satisfied with your question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.77,1:28:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.77,1:28:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.11,1:28:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.56,1:28:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.47,1:28:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.47,1:28:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.43,1:28:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a treat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.52,1:28:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.52,1:28:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.52,1:28:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.81,1:28:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to sign this?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.81,1:28:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.81,1:28:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.15,1:28:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your presence here in this lifetime, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.15,1:28:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of us who can be here and not be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.15,1:28:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.15,1:28:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.96,1:28:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to know two things.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.96,1:28:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could give us an om, sing an om for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.40,1:28:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Om.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.40,1:29:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To bless me and those that I love for this new life that has started in part due to my
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.64,1:29:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.64,1:29:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hear anything you're saying now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.64,1:29:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.64,1:29:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to bless me and those that I love.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.64,1:29:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got through doing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.64,1:29:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.64,1:29:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.64,1:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the om.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.64,1:29:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.64,1:29:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.64,1:29:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.64,1:29:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.73,1:29:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.73,1:29:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.18,1:29:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.18,1:29:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.18,1:29:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.18,1:29:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.69,1:29:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.77,1:29:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.89,1:29:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.89,1:29:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.89,1:29:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.34,1:29:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am afraid to hug people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.34,1:29:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.34,1:29:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.34,1:29:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.34,1:29:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said no hugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.50,1:29:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.46,1:29:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.46,1:29:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.46,1:29:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, Maria, the Mexican who's been coming here for many years, she asked me to say
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.73,1:29:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,hello from Canada where she's now living.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.73,1:29:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.73,1:29:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kamloops, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.73,1:29:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And she wanted to know if you have written, have a book of poetry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.73,1:29:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.73,1:29:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.73,1:30:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.73,1:30:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.73,1:30:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.73,1:30:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.73,1:30:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.73,1:30:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.73,1:30:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.73,1:30:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.73,1:30:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.73,1:30:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.73,1:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.73,1:30:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.73,1:30:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.73,1:30:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.73,1:30:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.73,1:30:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.73,1:30:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.73,1:30:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to have a book of poetry that you've written.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.73,1:30:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.73,1:30:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.73,1:30:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she reads your prose and she says, oh, you've gotta have a poetry
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.73,1:30:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,book.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.73,1:30:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.73,1:30:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sissies.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.22,1:30:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm realing then.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.00,1:30:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, them poetry types.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.31,1:30:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys don't go over poetry thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.75,1:30:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I played violin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.78,1:30:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.93,1:30:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.17,1:30:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.17,1:31:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is, I've been re-reading Transcending the Levels, and what I've noticed
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.82,1:31:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in reading the first, the lower levels, that I see in myself still, where there's times
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.72,1:31:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when I say, I can't, and where I am still, those things, those aversions and those attractions
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.77,1:31:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.77,1:31:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.77,1:31:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote the book, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.77,1:31:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.00,1:31:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.00,1:31:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the thing that I saw for myself, because you go, oh my God, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.64,1:31:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, okay, really, I'm witnessing and observing this, I just need to step back and
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.88,1:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,not be identified.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.88,1:31:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.88,1:31:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, and just say, oh, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.88,1:31:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.88,1:31:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.88,1:31:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.00,1:31:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.00,1:31:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And just, I find, then, just something else that's been in my head was the whole, the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.39,1:32:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,thing of surrender, like, I, all my life, I have felt a thing of surrendering, and I've,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.72,1:32:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been times when I just go out and I lay on the earth and just, you know, raise
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.68,1:32:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my hands, like, and just, there's never been a feeling that it is enough, and I'm wonder,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.18,1:32:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,um.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.18,1:32:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.34,1:32:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.34,1:32:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to keep surrendering, and.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.34,1:32:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.34,1:32:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.34,1:32:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you start crawling on your knees all the way to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.25,1:32:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.25,1:32:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.25,1:32:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.25,1:32:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.25,1:32:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.25,1:32:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.25,1:32:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.36,1:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.36,1:32:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was led here just a little over a year ago to discover you and your work, and have
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.36,1:32:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,been coming to your seminars as the ones I could get into ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.36,1:32:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.36,1:32:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.36,1:32:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.22,1:33:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.07,1:33:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.07,1:33:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.07,1:33:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.07,1:33:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.07,1:33:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.07,1:33:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.07,1:33:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.07,1:33:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.07,1:33:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.07,1:33:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.07,1:33:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.07,1:33:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,dining in.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.07,1:33:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And reading your books, um, and re-reading them, as part of my daily practice, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.28,1:33:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is we're, virtually every day I read some of your, or re-read some of your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.94,1:33:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been so powerful that, um, after about six months, and then about right around
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.21,1:33:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,my 60th birthday, I experienced what I felt was truly a rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.71,1:33:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.94,1:33:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh, so I get, in a, in a sort of a reversal state.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.18,1:33:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.34,1:33:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,adoption, I guess I've discovered that you're my spiritual father, and with all the love
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.10,1:33:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and honor and respect that that accords. And so I feel that I've really, through both your
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.44,1:34:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,efforts and the grace of God, I feel I've at least saved a few lifetimes of effort,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.60,1:34:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and made this one immeasurably more pleasurable, enjoyable. And so I thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.97,1:34:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have two questions, a small one and a large one. The small one is, in a couple of your books,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.25,1:34:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as it was mentioned today, you mentioned the fact that beings are born with a
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.52,1:34:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,calibratable consciousness level. I suppose that entails, then, that we come into this world
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.44,1:34:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with a calibratable consciousness level. And I suppose that entails, then, that we
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.59,1:34:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,come into this world with the consciousness level that we had when we left the last life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.86,1:34:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the implication. But there's other inner fields where we could go in the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.05,1:34:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you may have made the progress there, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.18,1:34:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. And the larger question that concerns me is that about a month or two after this,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.59,1:35:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what I call a rebirth, my wife went back into rehab, alcoholic rehab, for the fourth time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.02,1:35:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And has been there five months. And after stage two, which is supposed to get into deeper issues,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.02,1:35:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,she came back and failed immediately, and so went back. And by that time, I had the confidence in
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.32,1:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your kinesiology approach that I, for the first time, used that method to explore the possible
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.56,1:35:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,underlying issues that would have caused that failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.02,1:35:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And discovered a sexual transgression at the age of three and a half. And what I'm bothered with is that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.39,1:35:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if with this, what I consider truth, because of what I've read, from a moral standpoint, am I morally
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.14,1:35:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,obligated to do anything with this truth, or to not do anything with this truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.48,1:35:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.19,1:36:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Do nothing? I mean, I shouldn't make this...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.55,1:36:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I shouldn't make this so-called truth available to my wife, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.55,1:36:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it's going to be of any benefit. It's not going to be of any benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.55,1:36:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's in psychoanalysis, that's something different. And the memory comes up, the repressed unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.22,1:36:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But to hear it from an external source, there's a principle in psychoanalysis, an interpretation made outside of the therapeutic relationship is always taken as an attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.30,1:36:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.46,1:36:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.61,1:36:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she's laying on your couch paying you to interpret back, it'll be acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.61,1:36:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a spontaneous presentation from you, she'll probably give you some bad words about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.61,1:36:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be true of the perpetrator as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.10,1:36:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.47,1:36:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.73,1:37:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Other forces are going to have to deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.73,1:37:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.73,1:37:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.73,1:37:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That helps me a great deal. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.73,1:37:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.73,1:37:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a grave situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.73,1:37:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And it's, you know, there's children involved in the suffering process.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.73,1:37:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah. I'll give you a...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.73,1:37:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was wondering, if there's something I should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.73,1:37:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to say, keep as clear of it as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.73,1:37:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.73,1:37:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reveal everything you know in this world. If I did, I wouldn't be here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.64,1:37:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be put away as bad long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.64,1:37:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.64,1:37:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the other thing I enjoy. The spirituality with humor is just remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.64,1:37:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.64,1:37:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.64,1:37:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think humor is a very great spiritual benefit. It allows you to accept things that you would never accept otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.73,1:37:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.73,1:38:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can detach and accept it. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.64,1:38:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to take a picture, if I could, of you and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.64,1:38:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.68,1:38:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, two. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.35,1:38:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.75,1:38:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.75,1:38:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're done?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.75,1:38:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One more question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.75,1:38:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.75,1:38:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.06,1:38:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.06,1:38:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.06,1:38:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.14,1:38:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, David and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.43,1:38:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a little, I feel almost selfish asking a question, but along my travels, I'm part Native American,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.43,1:38:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the sweat ceremony in this one place we've been going from time to time, year to year,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.43,1:38:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we dipped into a spring beside us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.43,1:38:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ancient ground by the people in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.43,1:39:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one time that I still am looking for an explanation of what happened, it was as if my consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.43,1:39:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when I dipped in the water, my consciousness left my body, and I was as if suspended in the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.43,1:39:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and it brought a sense of panic at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.43,1:39:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I asked my wife, am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.43,1:39:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my heart beating?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.43,1:39:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.43,1:39:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I just laid back and spent, I don't know how long, drifting in what appeared as clouds, very peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.43,1:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then calmly came back, and we went on our way, actually went back in the sweat again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.43,1:39:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, what happens when these kind of things happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.43,1:39:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could say it's generally out of body experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.50,1:39:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you went to a different location, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.50,1:39:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.50,1:39:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a vital location.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.50,1:39:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an out-of-body experience, and it sounds like a rather pleasant and beautiful one, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.52,1:40:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.52,1:40:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world around seems to change as a consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.32,1:40:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's you that's changed, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.59,1:40:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.59,1:40:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a lovely experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.88,1:40:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.88,1:40:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.06,1:40:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's a fine experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.06,1:40:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.06,1:40:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.06,1:40:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.23,1:40:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Great question.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.52,1:40:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.52,1:40:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.52,1:40:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one miracle I forgot to mention, and he just brought it up, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.52,1:40:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the top of Schnebly Hill when I first came out west here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.52,1:40:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a place there for sale, the top of Schnebly Hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.63,1:40:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And 90 acres for sale, and I think there was a lake and all, and some buildings.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.63,1:40:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I looked at it several times.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.65,1:40:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And one night I had a dream of stepping over a serpent.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.64,1:40:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was several months prior.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.64,1:41:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I was on top of Schnebly Hill, and I'm looking through these buildings, and there's
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.64,1:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.64,1:41:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's 90 acres of nobody, and just a couple of buildings.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.64,1:41:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I stepped over a step, there was a huge rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.64,1:41:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, a great big rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.64,1:41:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's pulled back, and he's ready to strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.86,1:41:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant, I surrendered to God, like in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.40,1:41:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In a state of profound peace, the state of peace is enormously powerful, enormously soft,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.63,1:41:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and enormously powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.63,1:41:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Time stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.63,1:41:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Time stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.76,1:41:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The snake was totally suspended by the energy, and I was suspended.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.10,1:41:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were both outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.10,1:41:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In clock time, we looked at each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.52,1:41:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen a rattlesnake before.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.52,1:41:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'd never seen a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.52,1:42:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So we looked into each other's souls and felt completely safe with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.97,1:42:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because we were both suspended by this infinite power of peace, prevailing peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.97,1:42:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This lasted for minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.13,1:42:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Minutes, two of us suspended in time in complete and utter safety with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.11,1:42:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was taking in the beingness of the snake,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.11,1:42:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was taking in the beingness of this human.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.11,1:42:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never seen a human before.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.11,1:42:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And this went on for a considerable length of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.27,1:42:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,this enormous state of peace and safety, absolute safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.43,1:42:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the snake was satisfied, and he went away and shook his little tail as he went away.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.43,1:42:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like he had the camera on stop, and then somebody pushed the start button,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.43,1:42:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and then life sort of started again.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.43,1:42:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was an interesting experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.43,1:42:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to recalibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.43,1:42:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.43,1:43:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The field that surrounded us was over 600, 700, 610.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.34,1:43:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.68,1:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so it's like when I was sitting on the rock one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.68,1:43:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.76,1:43:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The state of 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.76,1:43:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that was a very interesting experience
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.76,1:43:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're just corroborating the experiential reality of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.17,1:43:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we all started joining in experiences now and did a workshop on it,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.17,1:43:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we would recall all kinds of events that when you realized what it was,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.17,1:43:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it was actually the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.17,1:43:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the snake didn't change his mind, and neither did I,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.64,1:43:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's why we both lived to tell the tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.64,1:43:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I also saw that an instant of fear, one instant of fear would have cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.64,1:43:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was struck just like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.64,1:43:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have sensed one flicker of fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.64,1:43:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the presence of God prevailed as the infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.68,1:44:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the dream that I had now was fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.68,1:44:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am stepping over the serpent just like it happened in the dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.68,1:44:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in prophetic dreams in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.68,1:44:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the only one that ever came near by that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.68,1:44:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, it's been a wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.06,1:44:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Christmas almost.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.06,1:44:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.93,1:44:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.06,1:44:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for these thy gifts,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.25,1:44:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for these thy gifts that sit before me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.25,1:44:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What more greater gift could a teacher have than such wondrous students?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.25,1:44:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.25,1:44:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for your presence because you're God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.25,1:44:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wish you Merry Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.25,1:44:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I accept your presence as your gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.25,1:44:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel well loved by you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.25,1:44:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.96,1:45:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.47,1:45:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get together for a satsang next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.47,1:46:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The blessing of Almighty God be on you now,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.22,1:46:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.43,1:46:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.11,1:46:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My blessing goes with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.42,1:46:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.40,1:46:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.40,1:46:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to trip on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.50,1:46:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.50,1:46:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.50,1:46:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.50,1:47:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.77,1:47:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like the serpent under the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.77,1:47:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.77,1:47:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they cannot move.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.77,1:47:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see them?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.77,1:47:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot move.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.86,1:47:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The same energy field that held the serpent holds all of you right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.86,1:47:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to get loose?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.86,1:47:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,.
