Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.68,1:48:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.68,1:48:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with us. The Christ child is within the heart of all of us. Christmas is the rebirth of the
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.68,1:49:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ child within each one of us. God bless you. Let's get your mic off. Let's take you
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.28,1:49:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,electronically off. Okay. Isn't that adorable? Look at this. Thank you so much. You can take
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.39,1:49:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,my microphone off. This bear was the finisher. If my child wasn't up before, it was up now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.05,1:50:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after the child and me, I'll tell you. Everything's lit up at Christmas time. We have
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.55,1:50:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas lights all around everything. All the little buildings are lit up, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.90,1:51:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of fun. What do we got here? What's this green thing? We've got quite a few praying
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.47,1:51:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,mantises in the greenhouse right now. We've got some big praying mantises in the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.22,1:51:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a leaf and I was going to brush it off. It's a great big praying mantis.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.65,1:51:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As big as they get. She looks like this, you know. I scared her. It's all right.
